Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.74,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好漂亮喔    是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.82,0:00:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快进去吧     两位好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.36,0:00:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是有订房的上原    505号房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.57,0:00:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面请\N只有一个房间？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.77,0:00:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N你们公司只订了一个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.58,0:00:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.05,0:01:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起住？    有空的房间吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.12,0:01:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经客满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.93,0:01:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麽办      现在是旺季
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.74,0:01:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太可能有空房间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.09,0:01:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗.....\N今天天也刚好客满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.63,0:01:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.97,0:01:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.31,0:02:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们先去了     希望房间大一点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.66,0:02:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满大的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.86,0:02:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错       真的很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.34,0:02:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.81,0:02:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边住真棒\N可是只有一个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.15,0:02:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊，不要想那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.36,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.51,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这裎贡的很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.92,0:03:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去洗澡了    嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.20,0:03:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣呢？找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.94,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.20,0:06:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.85,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服      是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.58,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.72,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉很棒吗    棒极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.92,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要泡吗     我待会再去泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.80,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝茶吧         这里真的不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.01,0:07:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找情人来一起住不错      我也这么觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真是有点那个    对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.50,0:07:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.77,0:07:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好在一起睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是，真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.79,0:07:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没办法啊     真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.86,0:07:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会介意吗    是不会啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.00,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是        别想那麽多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.48,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们睡一晚，明天再找他旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.29,0:08:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会担心吗    有前辈在是不会担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.84,0:08:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.51,0:08:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是.....   睡一晚就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.26,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的其他办法了     你别再'想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样办吧    怎么办....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.89,0:09:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.29,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.03,0:09:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太近了啦      会吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我离开一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.32,0:10:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好了吧     还是太近了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来      你怕什麽，我又不会怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.01,0:10:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我是什么人啦      好吧，那我先睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.44,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.51,0:14:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的睡着了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.26,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤露出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.26,0:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好弹的屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.09,0:23:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.90,0:24:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.97,0:24:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.26,0:24:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一下就好      不要，你做什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.87,0:24:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.28,0:24:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.33,0:25:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.16,0:26:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.23,0:26:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.58,0:26:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想要的    等等....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.98,0:26:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别弄我的奶头     很敏感吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.66,0:26:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.41,0:26:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敏感喔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.29,0:27:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很敏感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.03,0:27:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.44,0:27:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我那柽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.78,0:27:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.38,0:27:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你很想要吧    没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.52,0:27:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麽湿了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.26,0:27:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.47,0:28:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家会有感觉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.67,0:28:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好好享受啊      不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.02,0:28:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.50,0:28:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞    有什麽好害羞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.24,0:28:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小     别说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:43.25,0:28:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太赞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.58,0:28:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.34,0:29:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.24,0:29:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.71,0:29:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.20,0:30:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:18.14,0:30:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先等一下    我要继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.03,0:30:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这麽硬了，感觉到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:42.43,0:30:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.57,0:30:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的屁股好淫荡     别说这种话好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.51,0:31:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:03.25,0:31:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.43,0:31:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽   你湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.03,0:31:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:02.38,0:32:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.25,0:32:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.27,0:32:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的好湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:24.40,0:32:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.94,0:32:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.75,0:32:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:53.76,0:32:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太赞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.78,0:33:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.87,0:33:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:36.07,0:33:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要吗     我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.36,0:33:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.57,0:34:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:11.84,0:34:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很奇怪耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:31.60,0:34:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:56.02,0:35:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.72,0:35:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以帮我乳交吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.93,0:35:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦      又没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.01,0:35:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.62,0:36:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.09,0:36:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:10.76,0:36:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉捧好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.37,0:36:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:35.99,0:36:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.13,0:36:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:54.94,0:37:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.41,0:37:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.96,0:37:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样射可以吗     不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.10,0:37:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用戴套了，直接干进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.38,0:37:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是.....你也忍不住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.98,0:37:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，不用了     你说的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.80,0:37:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.42,0:38:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.62,0:38:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.64,0:38:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶得好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.85,0:38:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.86,0:38:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.94,0:39:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.22,0:39:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.70,0:39:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.84,0:39:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.92,0:39:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽到受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.53,0:40:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:32.89,0:40:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:54.78,0:40:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:57.58,0:41:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.28,0:41:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好爽    是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.43,0:41:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.64,0:42:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.39,0:42:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.70,0:42:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.11,0:43:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.65,0:43:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.80,0:43:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.01,0:43:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:55.23,0:43:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶得好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:08.71,0:44:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴爽翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.51,0:44:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续干我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:21.65,0:44:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用力点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.32,0:44:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:29.53,0:44:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快忍不住了    真的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:40.20,0:44:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:44.88,0:44:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.75,0:44:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行    快射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:58.89,0:45:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:01.16,0:45:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绐我更多   来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:33.99,0:45:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会中出了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:36.93,0:45:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没戴套的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.40,0:45:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，真的忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:48.94,0:45:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎麽办     去洗澡就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:00.28,0:46:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是危脸期吗    不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:05.62,0:46:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:13.36,0:46:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽就好了，别想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:25.64,0:46:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:29.38,0:46:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你生气吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:32.18,0:46:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:43.13,0:46:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着你的没其他房间吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.86,0:46:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问了，真的没有    是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:57.54,0:47:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩这房间了    打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.82,0:47:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:19.30,0:47:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:26.37,0:47:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的安排不了     其他房间给二位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.58,0:47:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没房间了？   嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:41.45,0:47:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麽办   这边有其他旅馆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:48.66,0:47:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边就只有我一家-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.60,0:48:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上是周末    就算找到旅馆也是客满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:19.76,0:48:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.83,0:48:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是同事，不能一起睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:31.90,0:48:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想想法好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:39.64,0:48:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱不是问题     抱歉，真是的没房间了=
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:04.87,0:49:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有仓库类的    我睡那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:14.75,0:49:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麽夸张了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:22.89,0:49:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也没办法，那就算，一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:37.30,0:49:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次别这样好吗     非常抱歉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:49.05,0:49:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怪他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:51.18,0:49:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是我们不对，很抱歉歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:03.33,0:50:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天12点就有空房间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:10.40,0:50:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请二位体谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:20.01,0:50:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用再道歉了     那我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:26.15,0:50:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有茶吗    马上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:36.69,0:50:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法呢，这也不能怪他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:46.17,0:50:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:51.11,0:50:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快洗澡睡觉吧    嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:58.45,0:51:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我准备明天会议的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:32.62,0:51:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的晚餐满好吃的     我也觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:38.62,0:51:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实服务也不错       是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:49.03,0:51:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去准备好资料    那我先睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:59.84,0:52:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天几点起床？    7点就要起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:08.25,0:52:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:03.64,0:53:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡箸了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:08.31,0:53:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗织小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:56.11,1:00:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:59.32,1:01:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:06.66,1:01:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这麽一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:17.07,1:01:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:22.81,1:01:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就结束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:45.50,1:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:22.33,1:02:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.08,1:02:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要是做了    就回不去的.....·
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.95,1:02:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就今天而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:20.26,1:03:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:31.74,1:03:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一次又不会怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:07.90,1:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行......不要舔那裎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:18.18,1:04:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:30.06,1:04:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不舒服.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:57.82,1:05:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:11.03,1:05:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔那我们会受不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:49.21,1:05:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:59.28,1:07:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说出去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:02.61,1:07:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.91,1:07:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:34.64,1:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:57.73,1:08:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也让我爽     嘴巴别停下来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:48.19,1:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:51.66,1:08:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:59.40,1:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被别人知道怎麽办     不会有人知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:13.41,1:09:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:19.15,1:09:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只有今天喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:32.90,1:09:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:18.14,1:10:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗       爽翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:30.29,1:10:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的受不了，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:54.98,1:11:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了       还是不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:01.79,1:11:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:05.26,1:11:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:22.34,1:11:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没戴套的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:28.35,1:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再弄我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:35.82,1:11:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:45.56,1:11:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先停下来     我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:51.30,1:12:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没套，不要再弄我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.45,1:12:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你停下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:06.78,1:12:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:09.85,1:12:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:13.32,1:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:17.19,1:12:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有感觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:24.67,1:12:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:33.21,1:12:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:15.92,1:13:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来    已经停不下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:26.60,1:13:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行.....我会受不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:38.08,1:13:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:53.82,1:13:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:11.98,1:14:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:19.58,1:14:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:34.13,1:14:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:26.45,1:15:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:53.28,1:15:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:55.95,1:15:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:26.91,1:16:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽死人家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:43.73,1:16:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不行？好舒服.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:49.33,1:16:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴爽翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:12.29,1:17:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这麽用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:29.11,1:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:32.04,1:17:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:48.33,1:17:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:53.00,1:17:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:26.63,1:18:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行    中出喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:50.25,1:18:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:56.59,1:20:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:15.94,1:20:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用力摇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:34.09,1:20:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:46.10,1:20:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:45.50,1:21:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:21.67,1:22:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:27.06,1:23:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了，高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:30.73,1:24:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:41.41,1:24:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，我要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:09.09,1:26:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:13.76,1:26:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，有人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:16.43,1:26:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了     抱歉这么晚来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:22.97,1:26:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:28.45,1:26:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:31.52,1:26:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了，找到旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:45.93,1:26:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:49.27,1:26:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉这麽晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:56.74,1:27:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:10.49,1:27:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉今天只剩一个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:15.29,1:27:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩一间？   嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:23.83,1:27:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他旅馆都客满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:37.58,1:27:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们只剩一间了   是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:47.06,1:27:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉．
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:52.53,1:27:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能住一间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:59.87,1:28:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只剩一间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:11.75,1:28:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:14.55,1:28:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说只剩一间房间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:24.96,1:28:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说其他旅也满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:34.71,1:28:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:40.98,1:28:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麽看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:45.78,1:28:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住一晚应该没差吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:53.52,1:28:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然没地方睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:58.73,1:29:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没睡吧    真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:07.67,1:29:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:13.41,1:29:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快睡觉，明天还要早起开会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:25.29,1:29:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:29.56,1:29:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:38.90,1:29:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带两位进房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:50.78,1:30:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这间    还不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:04.53,1:30:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满大的    就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:14.40,1:30:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我紧张起来了    为什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:19.74,1:30:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们只是普通同事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:28.69,1:30:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想那麽多，今天我们出差而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:39.63,1:30:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别乱想喔     我是不会啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:50.97,1:30:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你男友知道怎麽办？      不要跟他说就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.45,1:31:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是公事出差         没别的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:12.33,1:31:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是，不过还是会紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:21.94,1:31:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当跟朋友一起就好，别想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:33.95,1:31:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的不介意？       有什麽好介意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:45.03,1:31:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己想多了       是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:57.84,1:32:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很爱乱想的   就叫你别想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:12.79,1:32:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我们要很早起    嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:27.47,1:32:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着还要跟部长报告    要报告今天的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:40.95,1:32:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起住的事就不用提了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:50.29,1:32:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去洗澡了    嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:55.77,1:33:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边吗            嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:06.04,1:33:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:09.91,1:33:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我累了    还有床铺吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:21.39,1:33:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没有啦      那我自己睡那边就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:44.08,1:33:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会冷吗      可是总不能一起睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:00.50,1:34:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样睡就好了    你会感冒啪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:13.44,1:34:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你一半     真的假的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:23.05,1:34:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是睡觉，你别想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:33.06,1:34:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来睡吧        你真的不介意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:48.95,1:34:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不会了，你很烦那
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:00.82,1:35:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很晚了，你快来睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:13.90,1:35:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不太好吧     睡一晚而已拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:24.58,1:35:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗        你不要乱来就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:39.53,1:35:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不介意了，你是男人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:51.54,1:36:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是女在都不介意了    好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:03.29,1:36:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不用了    我不管你了，感冒别怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:02.27,1:39:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还叫我一起睡，
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:06.14,1:39:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太赞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:06.27,1:39:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太赞了
