Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:07.20,1:39:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太赞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:07.47,1:39:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太赞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:47.74,1:45:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:54.32,1:48:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:07.54,1:49:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:16.88,1:49:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么湿湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:21.42,1:49:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麽？    没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:30.49,1:49:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这味道....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:37.83,1:49:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会打手枪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:47.58,1:49:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思     不行这样喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:58.79,1:50:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧      才不要捶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:13.20,1:50:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趁我睡箸自己爽完就算了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:25.22,1:50:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又有爽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:35.76,1:50:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:40.03,1:50:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:46.57,1:50:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:50.97,1:50:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不想要？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:58.45,1:51:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才做了什麽？    我要以牙还牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:11.26,1:51:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:16.60,1:51:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄我就可以喔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:29.95,1:51:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边，又硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:38.09,1:51:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行     你明明想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:49.83,1:51:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样睡觉太可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:00.24,1:52:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好多爱液
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:17.19,1:52:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才对我了什麽？没有....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:35.35,1:52:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:02.17,1:53:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:08.98,1:53:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡的謦音
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:13.25,1:53:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了？射出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:33.40,1:53:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想这样吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:40.34,1:53:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:45.68,1:53:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你想干我吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:59.96,1:54:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:08.24,1:54:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:03.23,1:55:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着和我推车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:27.65,1:55:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太激烈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:39.46,1:56:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是很硬耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:39.25,1:57:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:42.32,1:57:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:48.19,1:57:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又射了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:52.20,1:57:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你吸干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:12.35,1:58:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才在弄我      为什麽突然射了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:21.29,1:58:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你太性感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:26.36,1:58:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧，不过先帮我擦干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:37.71,1:58:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:39.98,1:58:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:44.38,1:58:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先帮我擦干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:51.05,1:58:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黏黏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:55.99,1:59:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:08.67,1:59:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很热耶   我要睡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:22.95,1:59:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是先去洗澡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:29.89,1:59:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管你了，我要睡了
